404
00:38:51,066 --> 00:38:53,300
Let's make a promise, like this.

405
00:38:59,834 --> 00:39:02,567
Grandma, we'll meet again.

406
00:39:02,633 --> 00:39:06,533
My name is Ri Moon-seong.
Don't forget me.

407
00:39:19,700 --> 00:39:23,166
