tightly around mine.

411
00:39:43,500 --> 00:39:45,533
I can't…

412
00:39:48,433 --> 00:39:51,166
forget that feeling.

413
00:39:53,100 --> 00:39:55,100
Twenty years is a long time.

414
00:39:57,200 --> 00:39:59,700
Do you think that child's grasp

415
00:39:59,800 --> 00:40:02,734
